<h2 id="next-steps">E. Next Steps</h2>
<p>
  Based on the findings of this report, we recommend the following next steps:
</p>
<ol>
  <li>Review the recommended measures and prioritize implementation based on payback period and available budget.</li>
  <li>Develop an implementation plan for the selected measures.</li>
  <li>Explore available rebates and incentives to reduce implementation costs.</li>
  <li>Implement the selected measures and monitor results.</li>
  <li>Continue to track energy and water usage to verify savings.</li>
</ol>
